                  Mizuki - Wagyu Beef
┗━                    	•◦இ•◦               	━┛

☆ﾐ Mizuki is a sweetheart but she can be very fiery and passionate… especially late at night. 
Wagyu beef is refined but at the same time, soft and tender, just like Mizuki!

Mizuki enjoys sweets, cooking for her master and sophisticated talks.
Mizuki dislikes bugs, boring conversations and anyone who talks badly about master!

☆ﾐ “Why don’t you eat the beef while it’s hot, master? Mizuki is very upset that you don't…hpmm!”
